#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid "&microbe;"
msgstr "&microbe;"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction and General Syntax"
msgstr "Introducció i sintaxi general"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>Microbe</application> compiles programs written in the custom "
"language for PICs, as a companion program to &ktechlab;. The syntax has been "
"designed to suit a &flowcode; program. The syntax for running "
"<command>microbe</command> from the command line is: <programlisting>microbe "
"[options] [input.microbe] [output.asm]</programlisting> where options are:"
msgstr ""
"El <application>microbe</application> compila els programes escrits en el "
"llenguatge personalitzat per als PIC, com a programa complementari del "
"&ktechlab;. La sintaxi ha estat dissenyada per a adaptar-se a un programa de "
"&flowcode;. La sintaxi per a executar el <command>microbe</command> des de "
"la línia d'ordres és:"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>--show-source</function> - Puts each line of &microbe; source code "
"as a comment in the assembly output before the assembly instructions "
"themselves for that line."
msgstr ""
"<function>--show-source</function> &mdash; Col·loca cada línia des del codi "
"font de &microbe; com a un comentari a la sortida en assemblador abans de "
"les instruccions en assemblador per a aquesta línia."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>--no-optimize</function> - Prevent optimization of the "
"instructions generated from the source. Optimization is usually safe, and so "
"this option is mainly used for debugging."
msgstr ""
"<function>--no-optimize</function> &mdash; Evita l'optimització de les "
"instruccions generades des de la font. L'optimització sol ser segura, de "
"manera que aquesta opció és útil sobretot per a depurar."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The .microbe input file must identify the target PIC by inserting the PIC "
"name at the top of the .microbe file; &eg; the name of a PIC16F84 is "
"\"P16F84\"."
msgstr ""
"El fitxer d'entrada <filename class=\"extension\">.microbe</filename> haurà "
"d'identificar el PIC de destinació inserint el nom del PIC a la part "
"superior del fitxer, &pex;, el nom d'un PIC16F84 és «P16F84»."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple complete &microbe; program"
msgstr "Programa de &microbe; complet i senzill"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"P16F84\n"
"\n"
"a = 0\n"
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTA = a\n"
"        a = a + 1\n"
"}\n"
"until a == 5\n"
"\n"
"end"
msgstr ""
"P16F84\n"
"\n"
"a = 0\n"
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTA = a\n"
"        a = a + 1\n"
"}\n"
"until a == 5\n"
"\n"
"end"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Naming conventions"
msgstr "Convencions de la nomenclatura"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following rules apply to variable names and labels:"
msgstr "Les regles següents s'apliquen als noms i etiquetes de les variables:"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They can only contain alphanumerical characters [a..z][A..Z][0..9] and the "
"underscore \"_\"."
msgstr ""
"Només poden contenir caràcters alfanumèrics [a..z][A..Z][0..9] i el guió "
"baix «_»."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "They are case-sensitive."
msgstr "Distingeixen entre majúscules i minúscules."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "They cannot start with a number."
msgstr "No poden començar amb un número."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They should not start with <quote>__</quote> (double underscore), as this is "
"reserved for use by the compiler."
msgstr ""
"No han de començar amb «__» (doble subratllat), ja que està reservat perquè "
"l'utilitzi el compilador."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bracing conventions"
msgstr "Convencions de les claus"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Curly braces, {}, indicate the start and end of a code block. They can "
"appear anywhere before the start and after the end of the code block. "
"Examples of acceptable code blocks:"
msgstr ""
"Les claus, {}, indiquen l'inici i el final d'un bloc de codi. Poden "
"aparèixer en qualsevol lloc abans de l'inici i després del final del bloc de "
"codi. Exemples de blocs de codi acceptables:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement1 {\n"
"        some code\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"sentència1 {\n"
"        algun codi\n"
"}"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement2 {\n"
"        other code }"
msgstr ""
"sentència2 {\n"
"        un altre codi }"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement3\n"
"{\n"
"        other code\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"sentència3\n"
"{\n"
"        un altre codi\n"
"}"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"statement5 {\n"
"        code block\n"
"} statement6"
msgstr ""
"sentència5 {\n"
"        bloc_de_codi\n"
"} sentència6"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commenting"
msgstr "Comentar"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Commenting is similar to C. // comments out the rest of the line. /* and */ "
"denote a multiline comment."
msgstr ""
"Comentar és similar a C. Les «//» comenten la resta de la línia. I les «/*» "
"i «*/» denoten un comentari de múltiples línies."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"// This is a comment\n"
"x = 2 \n"
"/* As is this\n"
"multiline comment */"
msgstr ""
"// Aquest és un comentari\n"
"x = 2 \n"
"/* Aquest és un comentari\n"
"de múltiples línies */"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Program Structure"
msgstr "Estructura del programa"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The PIC id must be inserted at the top of the program. The end of the main "
"program is denoted with <quote>end</quote>. Subroutines must placed after "
"<quote>end</quote>."
msgstr ""
"L'identificador PIC s'ha d'inserir a la part superior del programa. El final "
"del programa principal s'indica amb «end». Les subrutines s'han de col·locar "
"després de «end»."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subroutines"
msgstr "Subrutines"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "A subroutine can be called from anywhere in the code. Syntax:"
msgstr "Es pot cridar a una subrutina des de qualsevol part del codi. Sintaxi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sub SubName\n"
"{\n"
"        // Code...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"sub SubNom\n"
"{\n"
"        // Codi...\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The subroutine is called with <quote>call <replaceable>SubName</"
"replaceable></quote>."
msgstr "La subrutina es crida amb «call <replaceable>SubNom</replaceable>»."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "&microbe; language reference"
msgstr "Referència del llenguatge &microbe;"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:85 microbe.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>if</title>"
msgstr "<title>if</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Conditional branching. Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct\">if "
"[expression] then [statement]</programlisting> or <programlisting role="
"\"correct\">\n"
"if [expression] then\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}</programlisting> Similarly for else: <programlisting role=\"correct\">else "
"[statement]</programlisting> or"
msgstr ""
"Claus condicionals. Sintaxi: <programlisting role=\"correct\">if [expressió] "
"then [sentència]</programlisting> o <programlisting role=\"correct\">\n"
"if [expressió] then\n"
"{\n"
"        [bloc_de_sentències]\n"
"}</programlisting> De manera similar per a la resta: <programlisting role="
"\"correct\">else [sentència]</programlisting> o"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        [bloc_de_sentències]\n"
"}"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"if porta.0 is high then\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 200\n"
"}\n"
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 300\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"if porta.0 is high then\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 200\n"
"}\n"
"else\n"
"{\n"
"        delay 300\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "alias"
msgstr "alias"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aliases one string to another. Syntax:"
msgstr "L'àlies d'una cadena a una altra. Sintaxi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "alias [from] [to]"
msgstr "alias [des de] [a]"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "repeat"
msgstr "repeat"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Executes the statement block repeatedly until expression evaluates to true. "
"The evaluation of the expression is performed after the statement block, so "
"the statement block will always be executed at least once. Syntax:"
msgstr ""
"Executa el bloc de sentències repetidament fins que l'expressió s'avalua com "
"a certa. L'avaluació de l'expressió es realitza després del bloc de "
"sentències, de manera que el bloc de sentències sempre s'executarà almenys "
"una vegada. Sintaxi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}\n"
"until [expression]"
msgstr ""
"repeat\n"
"{\n"
"        [bloc_de_sentències]\n"
"}\n"
"until [expressió]"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "while"
msgstr "while"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to repeat, this repeatedly executes the statement block. However, "
"the expression is evaluated before execution, not after. So if the "
"expression evaluates to false on the first pass, then the statement block "
"will not get executed. Syntax:"
msgstr ""
"Similar a «repeat», això executarà repetidament el bloc de sentències. No "
"obstant això, l'expressió s'avaluarà abans de l'execució, no després. "
"Llavors, si l'expressió s'avalua com a falsa en el primer pas, el bloc de "
"sentències no s'executarà. Sintaxi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"while [expression]\n"
"{\n"
"        [statement block]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"while [expressió]\n"
"{\n"
"        [bloc_de_sentències]\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:132 microbe.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "goto"
msgstr "goto"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes execution of the code to continue at the next statement after "
"the label specified. Goto syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>goto</function> [labelname]</programlisting> Label syntax: "
"<programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>labelname:</function></"
"programlisting> It is often considered good programming practice to avoid "
"the use of goto. Use of control statements and subroutines will result in a "
"much more readable program."
msgstr ""
"Això fa que l'execució del codi continuï en la següent sentència després de "
"l'etiqueta especificada. Sintaxi de «goto»: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>goto</function> [nom_etiqueta]</programlisting> Sintaxi de "
"l'etiqueta: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>nom_etiqueta:</"
"function></programlisting> Sovint es considera una bona pràctica de "
"programació evitar l'ús de «goto». L'ús de sentències de control i "
"subrutines donarà com a resultat un programa molt més llegible."

# skip-rule: t-sp_pu
#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"goto MyLabel\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"[MyLabel]:\n"
"// Code will continue at this point"
msgstr ""
"goto Etiqueta_meva\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"[Etiqueta_meva]:\n"
"// El codi continuarà en aquest punt"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "call"
msgstr "call"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Calls a subroutine. Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>call</"
"function> [SubName]</programlisting> where <replaceable>SubName</"
"replaceable> is the name of the subroutine to be called."
msgstr ""
"Crida a una subrutina. Sintaxi: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>call</function> [SubNom]</programlisting> on "
"<replaceable>SubNom</replaceable> és el nom de la subrutina a cridar."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "delay"
msgstr "delay"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This causes the code execution to stop for the given period of time. The "
"interval is in milliseconds. Syntax:"
msgstr ""
"Fa que s'aturi l'execució del codi durant el període de temps especificat. "
"L'interval serà en mil·lisegons. Sintaxi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "<function>delay</function> [interval]"
msgstr "<function>delay</function> [interval]"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At present, &microbe; assumes that the PIC is operating at a frequency of "
"4MHz - &ie; each instruction takes 1 microsecond to execute. If this is not "
"the case, the interval must be adjusted proportionately."
msgstr ""
"En l'actualitat, el &microbe; assumeix que el PIC està operant a una "
"freqüència de 4 MHz, &ead;, cada instrucció triga 1 microsegon a executar-"
"se. Si aquest no és el cas, l'interval s'haurà d'ajustar proporcionalment."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "sevenseg"
msgstr "sevenseg"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to define the pin mapping for a (common cathode) seven segment "
"display connected to the PIC. Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>sevenseg</function> [name] [a] [b] [c] [d] [e] [f] [g]</"
"programlisting> where [a]...[g] are the PIC pins to which the respective "
"segments of the seven segment display are attached. The pins can be written "
"either as PORTX.N or RXN."
msgstr ""
"Això es fa servir per a definir l'assignació dels pins per a una pantalla de "
"set segments (càtode habitual) connectada al PIC. Sintaxi: <programlisting "
"role=\"correct\"><function>sevenseg</function> [nom] [a] [b] [c] [d] [e] [f] "
"[g]</programlisting> on [a]...[g] són els pins del PIC als quals s'adjunten "
"els segments respectius de la pantalla de set segments. Els pins es poden "
"escriure com a PORTX.N o RXN."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display a number on the seven segment, the pin mapping is treated as a "
"write only variable."
msgstr ""
"Per a mostrar un número en els set segments, l'assignació dels pins es "
"tracta com una variable de només escriptura."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining and outputting to a seven segment"
msgstr "Definició i sortida a un set segments"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"sevenseg seg1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"seg1 = x + 2"
msgstr ""
"sevenseg seg1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"seg1 = x + 2"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "keypad"
msgstr "keypad"

# skip-rule: t-sp_pu
#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to define the pin mapping for a keypad connected to the PIC. "
"Syntax: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>keypad</function> [name] "
"[row 1] ... [row 4] [column 1] ... [column n]</programlisting> where [row "
"1] ... [row 4] and [column 1] ... [column n] are the PIC pins to which the "
"respective rows and columns of the keypad are attached (at the moment, the "
"number of rows is not changeable). See <xref linkend=\"sevenseg\"/> (above) "
"for more information on pin mappings."
msgstr ""
"Això es fa servir per a definir l'assignació dels pins per a un teclat "
"numèric connectat al PIC. Sintaxi: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\"><function>keypad</function> [nom] [fila 1] ... [fila 4] [columna 1] ... "
"[columna n]</programlisting> on [fila 1] ... [fila 4] i [columna 1] ... "
"[columna n] són els pins del PIC als quals s'adjunten les respectives files "
"i columnes del teclat numèric (de moment, el nombre de files és no "
"modificable). Per a obtenir més informació sobre les assignacions dels pins, "
"vegeu la <xref linkend=\"sevenseg\"/> (a dalt)."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The columns of the keypad should be pulled down via 100k resistors to "
"ground. The row pins must be configured as outputs and the column pins as "
"inputs. Once the keypad has been defined, it is treated as a read only "
"variable."
msgstr ""
"Les columnes del teclat numèric s'han de baixar a terra mitjançant "
"resistències de 100 k. Els pins de la fila s'han de configurar com a "
"sortides i els pins de la columna com a entrades. Una vegada s'ha definit el "
"teclat numèric, es tractarà com una variable de només lectura."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defining and reading from a keypad"
msgstr "Definir i llegir des d'un teclat numèric"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"keypad keypad1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"x = keypad1"
msgstr ""
"keypad keypad1 RB0 RB1 RB2 RB3 RB4 RB5 RB6\n"
"x = keypad1"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the values returned for a keypad are: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para>The value of the number if it is a numeric key (1 to 3 along "
"top row; hexadecimal A to D down the fourth column and continuing for each "
"extra column).</para></listitem> <listitem><para>253 for the key in row 4, "
"column 1.</para></listitem> <listitem><para>254 for the key in row 4, column "
"3.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> These values can be redefined by using "
"the alias command, where the name of the key in row x, column y (rows and "
"columns starting at 1), is Keypad_x_y. For example, to give the star key on "
"a 4x3 keypad the value zero, the following alias would be used:"
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada, els valors retornats per un teclat numèric són: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para>El valor del nombre si és una tecla numèrica "
"(1 a 3 a la fila superior, hexadecimal des de l'A fins a la D a la quarta "
"columna i continuant per a cada columna addicional).</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>253 per a la tecla a la fila 4, columna 1.</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>254 per a la tecla a la fila 4, columna 3.</para></listitem> "
"</itemizedlist> Aquests valors es poden redefinir utilitzant l'ordre "
"«alies», on el nom de la tecla a la fila «x», columna «y» (files i columnes "
"que comencen amb 1), és «Keypad_x_y». Per exemple, per a donar-li el valor "
"zero a la tecla d'asterisc en un teclat numèric de 4x3, s'utilitzarà el "
"següent àlies:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aliasing a keypad key to a value"
msgstr "Assignar un valor a una tecla del teclat numèric"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "alias Keypad_4_1 0"
msgstr "alias Keypad_4_1 0"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "PIC I/O"
msgstr "E/S del PIC"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port Direction"
msgstr "Direcció del port"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The port direction is set by assigning a value to TRIS*, where * is the port "
"letter. For example:"
msgstr ""
"La direcció del port s'estableix assignant un valor a TRIS*, on «*» és la "
"lletra del port. Per exemple:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting port directions"
msgstr "Establint les direccions dels ports"

# skip-rule: t-apo_fim
#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "TRISB = b'01111001'"
msgstr "TRISB = b'01111001'"

# skip-rule: t-apo_fin
#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The above sets pins RB1, RB2 and RB7 on PORTB as outputs, and the other pins "
"on PORTB as inputs. In this example, b'01111001' is a binary representation "
"of the output type. The 1 on the right represents an output on RB0, and the "
"0 on the left represents an input on RB7."
msgstr ""
"L'anterior estableix els pins RB1, RB2 i RB7 a PORTB com a sortides i els "
"altres pins en PORTB com a entrades. En aquest exemple, b'01111001' és una "
"representació binària del tipus de sortida. L'1 de la dreta representa una "
"sortida a RB0 i el 0 de l'esquerra representa una entrada a RB7."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port I/O"
msgstr "E/S del port"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "The port can be treated as a variable. For example:"
msgstr "El port pot tractar-se com una variable. Per exemple:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Writing to a port"
msgstr "Escrivint a un port"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "x = PORTA"
msgstr "x = PORTA"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "The above assigns the value of PORTA to the variable x."
msgstr "Tot l'anterior assigna el valor de PORTA a la variable «x»."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pin I/O"
msgstr "E/S dels pins"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each pin on a port is obtained by prefixing the pin number by the port name; "
"&eg; Pin 2 (starting from Pin 0) on PORTA is known as <emphasis>PORTA.0</"
"emphasis>. The syntax to set a pin state is: <programlisting role=\"correct"
"\">PORTX.N = <emphasis>STATE</emphasis></programlisting> where "
"<emphasis>STATE</emphasis> can be <emphasis>high</emphasis> or "
"<emphasis>low</emphasis>. The syntax to test a pin state is: <programlisting "
"role=\"correct\"><function>if</function> PORTX.N is <emphasis>STATE</"
"emphasis> <function>then</function></programlisting> Combining these "
"examples, we have:"
msgstr ""
"Cada pin sobre un port s'obté anteposant el número del pin al nom del port, "
"&pex;, el pin 2 (començant pel pin 0) a PORTA es coneix com a "
"<emphasis>PORTA.0</emphasis>. La sintaxi per a establir un estat del pin és: "
"<programlisting role=\"correct\">PORTX.N = <emphasis>ESTAT</emphasis></"
"programlisting> on <emphasis>ESTAT</emphasis> pot ser <emphasis>high</"
"emphasis> o <emphasis>low</emphasis>. La sintaxi per a provar l'estat d'un "
"pin és: <programlisting role=\"correct\"><function>if</function> PORTX.N is "
"<emphasis>ESTAT</emphasis> <function>then</function></programlisting> "
"Combinant aquests exemples, tenim:"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting and testing pin state"
msgstr "Establint i provant l'estat dels pins"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"TRISA = 0\n"
"TRISB = 255\n"
"<function>if</function> PORTA.3 is <function>high</function> <function>then</"
"function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB.5 = <function>low</function>\n"
"}\n"
"<function>else</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB = PORTA + 15\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"TRISA = 0\n"
"TRISB = 255\n"
"<function>if</function> PORTA.3 is <function>high</function> <function>then</"
"function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB.5 = <function>low</function>\n"
"}\n"
"<function>else</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        PORTB = PORTA + 15\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variables"
msgstr "Variables"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All variables are 8-bit unsigned integers, giving a range from 0 to 255. "
"<application>&microbe;</application> supports the typical unary operations "
"(acting on one variable) and binary operations (acting on two variables) "
"that are supported by the PIC. In addition, &microbe; also supports division "
"and multiplication."
msgstr ""
"Totes les variables són enters de 8 bits sense signe, el qual dona un "
"interval des de 0 fins a 255. El <application>&microbe;</application> admet "
"les operacions unàries típiques (actuant sobre una variable) i les "
"operacions binàries (actuant sobre dues variables) que són admeses pel PIC. "
"A més, el &microbe; també admet la divisió i la multiplicació."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unary Operations"
msgstr "Operacions unàries"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>rotateleft x</emphasis> - Rotates the variable x left through "
"carry."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>rotateleft x</emphasis> &mdash; Gira la variable «x» cap a "
"l'esquerra a través del transport."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>rotateright x</emphasis> - Rotates the variable x right through "
"carry."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>rotateright x</emphasis> &mdash; Gira la variable «x» cap a la "
"dreta a través del transport."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>increment x</emphasis> - Increments the variable x. If x has a "
"value of 255, then x wraps round to 0."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>increment x</emphasis> &mdash; Augmenta la variable «x». Si «x» té "
"un valor de 255, llavors «x» s'arrodoneix a 0."

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>decrement x</emphasis> - Decrements the variable x. If x has a "
"value of 0, then x wraps round to 255."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>decrement x</emphasis> &mdash; Disminueix la variable «x». Si «x» "
"té un valor de 0, llavors «x» s'arrodoneix a 255."

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arithmetic"
msgstr "Aritmètica"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:293 microbe.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported operations:"
msgstr "Operacions admeses:"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Addition:</emphasis> x + y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Suma:</emphasis> x + y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Subtraction:</emphasis> x - y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Resta:</emphasis> x - y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Multiplication:</emphasis> x * y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Multiplicació:</emphasis> x * y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Division:</emphasis> x / y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Divisió:</emphasis> x / y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Binary XOR:</emphasis> x XOR y"
msgstr "<emphasis>XOR binari:</emphasis> x XOR y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Binary AND:</emphasis> x AND y"
msgstr "<emphasis>AND binari:</emphasis> x AND y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Binary OR:</emphasis> x OR y"
msgstr "<emphasis>OR binari:</emphasis> x OR y"

#. Tag: title
#: microbe.docbook:308 microbe.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparison"
msgstr "Comparació"

# skip-rule: barb-igual
#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Equals:</emphasis> x == y"
msgstr "<emphasis>Igual:</emphasis> x == y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Does not equal:</emphasis> x != y"
msgstr "<emphasis>No és igual:</emphasis> x != y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is greater than:</emphasis> x > y"
msgstr "<emphasis>És més gran que:</emphasis> x &gt; y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is less than:</emphasis> x &lt; y"
msgstr "<emphasis>És més petit que:</emphasis> x &lt; y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is greater than or equal to:</emphasis> x &gt;= y"
msgstr "<emphasis>És més gran o igual que:</emphasis> x &gt;= y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Is less than or equal to:</emphasis> x &lt;= y"
msgstr "<emphasis>És més petit o igual que:</emphasis> x &lt;= y"

#. Tag: para
#: microbe.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "Per exemple:"

# skip-rule: t-sp_pu
#. Tag: programlisting
#: microbe.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>if</function> PORTA >= 5 <function>then</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        ...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"<function>if</function> PORTA >= 5 <function>then</function>\n"
"{\n"
"        ...\n"
"}"
